  "remarks": "OJSC Machine-Building Plant Arsenal is a Russian military industry company. It fulfils Russian state defence orders and is engaged in the production of Lotos reconnaissance satellites and AK-176M naval guns. Lotos is used by the Russian Armed Forces in the war of aggression against Ukraine for target identification and AK-176M naval guns are installed in the Russian Navy ships that shell Ukrainian troops.",
